<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>@ViewBag.Title - SURFriends</title>
    <link href="~/Content/Site.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    <link href="~/Content/footer.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    <link href="~/Content/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    <script src="~/Scripts/modernizr-2.6.2.js"></script>
    <link href="https://fortawesome.github.io/Font-Awesome/assets/font-awesome/css/font-awesome.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="navbar navbar-inverse navbar-fixed-top">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="navbar-header">
                <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target=".navbar-collapse">
                    <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                    <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                    <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                </button>
                @Html.ActionLink("SURFriends", "Index", "Home", new { area = "" }, new { @class = "navbar-brand" })
            </div>
            <div class="navbar-collapse collapse">
                <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
                    <li class="dropdown">
                        <a href="#" class="dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" role="button" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">Fantasy<span class="caret"></span></a>
                        <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                            <li><a>Classificação Geral</a></li>
                            <li><a>Pagamentos</a></li>
                            <li><a>Regras</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container body-content">
        @RenderBody()
        <hr />
        <!--footer start from here-->
        <footer>
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 footerleft ">
                        <h6 class="heading7">Contatos</h6>                        
                        <p><i class="fa fa-map-pin"></i> Endereço Virtual</p>
                        <p><i class="fa fa-phone"></i> Fone : +55 (85)9 8832-0829</p>
                        <p><i class="fa fa-envelope"></i> E-mail : frutuozo29@gmail.com</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 paddingtop-bottom">
                        <h6 class="heading7">2Dev Tecnologia</h6>
                        <div class="post">
                            <p>Somos apaixonados por Desenvolvimento, por isso buscamos sempre aprender as novidades do mundo da tecnologia. Somos criativos, e sempre buscamos ajudar nossos clientes à alcançar seus objetivos. Desenvolvemos Aplicações Mobile, Web, Desktop, Sites, Lojas Virtuais.<span> Fortaleza, @DateTime.Now.ToString("dd MMMM yyyy")</span></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 paddingtop-bottom">
                        <h6 class="heading7">Social</h6>
                        <div class="fb-page" data-href="https://www.facebook.com/facebook" data-tabs="timeline" data-height="300" data-small-header="false" style="margin-bottom:15px;" data-adapt-container-width="true" data-hide-cover="false" data-show-facepile="true">
                            <blockquote cite="https://www.facebook.com/facebook"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/2devtecnologia/"><i class="fa fa-facebook-square" aria-hidden="true"></i> Facebook</a></blockquote>
                        </div>
                        <div class="" data-href="https://www.instagram.com/" data-tabs="timeline" data-height="300" data-small-header="false" style="margin-bottom:15px;" data-adapt-container-width="true" data-hide-cover="false" data-show-facepile="true">
                            <blockquote cite="https://www.instagram.com/"><a href="https://www.instagram.com/rfrutuozo/"><i class="fa fa-instagram" aria-hidden="true"></i> Instagram</a></blockquote>
                        </div>
                        <div class="" data-href="http://2dev.net.br" data-tabs="timeline" data-height="300" data-small-header="false" style="margin-bottom:15px;" data-adapt-container-width="true" data-hide-cover="false" data-show-facepile="true">
                            <blockquote cite="http://2dev.net.br"><a href="http://2dev.net.br"><i class="fa fa-rss" aria-hidden="true"></i> 2Dev Tecnologia</a></blockquote>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </footer>
        <!--footer start from here-->
        <div class="copyright">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <p>&copy; @DateTime.Now.Year - Developed by Renan Frutuozo</p>
                </div>                
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="~/Scripts/jquery-1.10.2.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/Scripts/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>